txt.en: 'One minute remaining until the game begins.'
'Please finish up! The game will end shortly.'
'Well done! The next game will begin in a few minutes. I hope to see you then!'
'We shall make another stand against the shrews very soon, friend.'
'Soon we shall do our best to drive off the shrews once more; they are likely to return in great numbers.'
